  "instructions": [
    "heat a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the ground beef and cook until browned, breaking it up into small pieces as it cooks.",
    "add the sliced onion and minced garlic and cook until softened.",
    "add the cumin, coriander, chili powder, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine.",
    "add the bay leaves and stir to combine.",
    "reduce heat to medium-low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "warm the tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "assemble the tacos by spooning the beef mixture onto a tortilla and topping with avocado, a squeeze of lime juice, and a spoonful of salsa."
